N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4101.30 - Filing of documents

State Regulations

The receipt by the commission for filing of any
document, contract, agreements or writings required to be filed with the
commission pursuant to law or the rules and regulations of this commission, shall not constitute an approval by the commission of the contents of such
documents, contracts, agreements or writings. Notes
